A SERIES OF VIGOROUS LOW PRESSURE SYSTEMS ARE FCST TO MOV
QCKY NE EITHER TO THE NW OF OR ACROSS THE N OF THE UK
THROUGH THIS FCST PERIOD. THE EXACT TRACK AND TIMING OF
